AssociateWebACL.name: AssociateWebACL
AssociateWebACL.description: Grants permission to associate a WebACL with a resource.

CheckCapacity.name: CheckCapacity
CheckCapacity.description:
Grants permission to calculate web ACL capacity unit (WCU) requirements for a specified
                                                scope and set of rules.

CreateIPSet.name: CreateIPSet
CreateIPSet.description: Grants permission to create an IPSet.

CreateRegexPatternSet.name: CreateRegexPatternSet
CreateRegexPatternSet.description: Grants permission to create a RegexPatternSet.

CreateRuleGroup.name: CreateRuleGroup
CreateRuleGroup.description: Grants permission to create a RuleGroup.

CreateWebACL.name: CreateWebACL
CreateWebACL.description: Grants permission to create a WebACL.

DeleteFirewallManagerRuleGroups.name: DeleteFirewallManagerRuleGroups
DeleteFirewallManagerRuleGroups.description:
Grants permission to delete specified FirewallManagedRulesGroups from the specified
                                                WebACL if not managed by Firewall Manager anymore.

DeleteIPSet.name: DeleteIPSet
DeleteIPSet.description: Grants permission to delete the specified IPSet.

DeleteLoggingConfiguration.name: DeleteLoggingConfiguration
DeleteLoggingConfiguration.description: Grants permission to delete the LoggingConfiguration from the specified WebACL.

DeletePermissionPolicy.name: DeletePermissionPolicy
DeletePermissionPolicy.description: Grants permission to delete the PermissionPolicy on the specified RuleGroup.

DeleteRegexPatternSet.name: DeleteRegexPatternSet
DeleteRegexPatternSet.description: Grants permission to delete the specified RegexPatternSet.

DeleteRuleGroup.name: DeleteRuleGroup
DeleteRuleGroup.description: Grants permission to delete the specified RuleGroup.

DeleteWebACL.name: DeleteWebACL
DeleteWebACL.description: Grants permission to delete the specified WebACL.

DescribeManagedRuleGroup.name: DescribeManagedRuleGroup
DescribeManagedRuleGroup.description: Grants permission to view high-level information for a managed rule group.

DisassociateFirewallManager.name: DisassociateFirewallManager
DisassociateFirewallManager.description: Grants permission to disassociate Firewall Manager from the specified WebACL.

DisassociateWebACL.name: DisassociateWebACL
DisassociateWebACL.description: Grants permission disassociate a WebACL from an application resource.

GetIPSet.name: GetIPSet
GetIPSet.description: Grants permission to view details about the specified IPSet.

GetLoggingConfiguration.name: GetLoggingConfiguration
GetLoggingConfiguration.description: Grants permission to view LoggingConfiguration about the specified WebACL.

GetPermissionPolicy.name: GetPermissionPolicy
GetPermissionPolicy.description: Grants permission to view PermissionPolicy on the specified RuleGroup.

GetRateBasedStatementManagedKeys.name: GetRateBasedStatementManagedKeys
GetRateBasedStatementManagedKeys.description: Grants permission to view the keys that are currently blocked by a rate-based rule.

GetRegexPatternSet.name: GetRegexPatternSet
GetRegexPatternSet.description: Grants permission to view details about the specified RegexPatternSet.

GetRuleGroup.name: GetRuleGroup
GetRuleGroup.description: Grants permission to view details about the specified RuleGroup.

GetSampledRequests.name: GetSampledRequests
GetSampledRequests.description:
Grants permission to view detailed information about a specified number of requests--a
                                                sample--that AWS WAF randomly selects from among the first 5,000 requests that your
                                                AWS resource received during a time range that you choose.

GetWebACL.name: GetWebACL
GetWebACL.description: Grants permission to view details about the specified GetWebACL.

GetWebACLForResource.name: GetWebACLForResource
GetWebACLForResource.description: Grants permission to view the WebACL for the specified resource.

ListAvailableManagedRuleGroups.name: ListAvailableManagedRuleGroups
ListAvailableManagedRuleGroups.description:
Grants permission to view an array of managed rule groups that are available for you
                                                to use.

ListIPSets.name: ListIPSets
ListIPSets.description:
Grants permission to view an array of IPSetSummary objects for the IP sets that you
                                                manage.

ListLoggingConfigurations.name: ListLoggingConfigurations
ListLoggingConfigurations.description: Grants permission to view an array of your LoggingConfiguration objects.

ListRegexPatternSets.name: ListRegexPatternSets
ListRegexPatternSets.description:
Grants permission to view an array of RegexPatternSetSummary objects for the regex
                                                pattern sets that you manage.

ListResourcesForWebACL.name: ListResourcesForWebACL
ListResourcesForWebACL.description:
Grants permission to view an array of the Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) for the resources
                                                that are associated with the specified web ACL.

ListRuleGroups.name: ListRuleGroups
ListRuleGroups.description:
Grants permission to view an array of RuleGroupSummary objects for the rule groups
                                                that you manage.

ListTagsForResource.name: ListTagsForResource
ListTagsForResource.description: Grants permission to lists tag for the specified resource.

ListWebACLs.name: ListWebACLs
ListWebACLs.description:
Grants permission to view an array of WebACLSummary objects for the web ACLs that
                                                you manage.

PutFirewallManagerRuleGroups.name: PutFirewallManagerRuleGroups
PutFirewallManagerRuleGroups.description: Grants permission to create FirewallManagedRulesGroups in the specified WebACL.

PutLoggingConfiguration.name: PutLoggingConfiguration
PutLoggingConfiguration.description:
Grants permission to enables the specified LoggingConfiguration, to start logging
                                                from a web ACL.

PutPermissionPolicy.name: PutPermissionPolicy
PutPermissionPolicy.description:
Grants permission to attach the specified IAM policy to the specified resource. The
                                                only supported use for this action is to share a RuleGroup across accounts.

TagResource.name: TagResource
TagResource.description: Grants permission to associates tags with the specified AWS resource.

UntagResource.name: UntagResource
UntagResource.description: Grants permission to disassociates tags from an AWS resource.

UpdateIPSet.name: UpdateIPSet
UpdateIPSet.description: Grants permission to update the specified IPSet.

UpdateRegexPatternSet.name: UpdateRegexPatternSet
UpdateRegexPatternSet.description: Grants permission to update the specified RegexPatternSet.

UpdateRuleGroup.name: UpdateRuleGroup
UpdateRuleGroup.description: Grants permission to update the specified RuleGroup.

UpdateWebACL.name: UpdateWebACL
UpdateWebACL.description: Grants permission to update the specified WebACL.
